---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout
  title="Getting Started"
  description="Install SignalPaper, run the local site, and understand what should be replaced before publishing."
>
  <h2>Install</h2>
  <pre><code>npm install
npm run dev</code></pre>

  <h2>Build</h2>
  <pre><code>npm run build
npm run preview</code></pre>

  <h2>Replace before publishing</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Update <code>src/config/site.ts</code>.</li>
    <li>Replace demo posts and projects.</li>
    <li>Set the production URL in both site configuration and Astro config.</li>
    <li>Enable newsletter, comments, or analytics only after adding real provider settings.</li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>

